
INSTALLING EMBER
    brew install node
      node -v
      npm -v
    npm install -g bower
    brew install watchman
    npm install -g ember-cli
    
EMBER PROJECT
    ember new project-name
    cd project-name
    ember serve or s or server    localhost:4200



    ember g route about  
    ember g model rental
    ember install emberfire
    ember g component rental-tile
    ember g component new-rental
    ember install ember-bootstrap
    
    
    Data down, actions up
    That means data like rentals names is pulled down from firebase while a button click action rises up from the components


